channel.title: Sheesh, these nulls are driving me nuts
channel.description:
Yes, I do know some coding, so don't call me a noob :D
Now...
to begin with my base is Deltascape of course, -.- now, heres the problem
What i've done: Added couple extra features, changed all the names of 'delta' to RSHQ - Mah server name.. Removed the anti-leech changed some tele's...
Then, I suddenly get this, which is driving me nuts. [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img529.imageshack.us/img529/6415/nullsft5.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://g.imageshack.us/img529/nullsft5.png/1/][IMG]http://img529.imageshack.us/img529/nullsft5.png/1/w659.png[/img][/URL]
http://img529.imageshack.us/my.php?image=nullsft5.png
Any luck trying to help? Also, i'm willing to upload the files if you'd like to see if theres anything you can figure to get it working..
